import React, { ReactText } from "react"
import { Flex } from "@chakra-ui/react"

import { Header, Sidebar } from "../../components"

export default function index({ children }) {
  return (
    <Flex direction="column" h="100vh">
      <Sidebar />
      <Flex w="100%" my="6" mx="auto" px="6">
        <Header />
        <Flex />
      </Flex>
    </Flex>
  )
}
